---
layout: base.njk
title: Fred Deichler — Agile Coach | International Speaker
description: Agile Coach with 13+ years experience coaching 50+ teams. Specializing in predictable delivery, flow metrics, and evidence-based management.
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <img src="IMG_3523.png" alt="Fred Deichler" class="avatar">
    <h1>Fred Deichler</h1>
    <p>Continuous Improvement Practitioner | International Speaker</p>
    <p><strong>I help organizations align people, product, and process using tailored patterns, not rigid frameworks.</strong></p>
    <p><em>13+ years driving results with data-backed insights.</em></p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/speaking/">View Speaking</a>
      <a class="btn outline" href="/contact/">Let's Connect</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="container">
  <!-- Recent Highlights Section -->
  <section class="card fade-in" style="background: var(--gradient-subtle); border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);">
    <h2>Recent Highlights</h2>
    <div id="recent-highlights-grid" class="grid three">
      {% set recentTalks = talks | sort(true, false, "date") | limit(3) %}
      {% for talk in recentTalks %}
        {% set isPast = talk.date | isPastDate %}
        <div class="card" style="padding: var(--space-lg);">
          <span class="badge">{% if isPast %}Recent{% else %}Upcoming{% endif %}</span>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-top: var(--space-sm);">{{ talk.event }} {{ talk.year }}</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);">{{ talk.title }}</p>
          <small style="color: var(--text-secondary);">{{ talk.date | shortDate }}</small>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I Help Teams -->
  <section class="grid two">
    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>How I Help Teams</h2>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>Improve delivery predictability from 55% to 88%+ through evidence-based metrics</li>
        <li>Reduce time-to-market with flow metrics and probabilistic forecasting</li>
        <li>Build sustainable practices with modern Agile and Lean methodologies</li>
        <li>Transform team effectiveness through AI integration and coaching</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="card fade-in">
      <h2>Speaking Topics</h2>
      <ul class="tight">
        <li>Predictable Delivery with EBM, Monte Carlo, Flow</li>
        <li>AI in Agile Teams</li>
        <li>Coaching with Triggers & Hooks</li>
        <li>Agile Transformation & Scaling</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card fade-in" id="home-testimonials">
    <h2>What People Say</h2>
    <div id="testimonials-grid" class="grid two">
      {% for q in testimonials | limit(6) %}
      <div class="quote">
        <p style="margin:0 0 .5rem 0">“{{ q.quote }}”</p>
        <small style="color:var(--text-secondary)">{{ q.event }}</small>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
